context:
The existing `empty_file()` function checks for empty file inputs:

r
empty_file <- function(x) {
  is.character(x) && length(x) == 1 && file.exists(x) &&
    file.info(x, extra_cols = FALSE)$size == 0
}


Current `read_file()` implementation:
r
read_file <- function(file, locale = default_locale()) {
  if (empty_file(file)) {
    return("")
  }
  # ... rest of function
}


Current `read_file_raw()` implementation:
r
read_file_raw <- function(file) {
  if (empty_file(file)) {
    return(raw())
  }
  # ... rest of function
}
